name: Hungry Hungry Henry
description:
Help feed Henry by catching different household objects but watch out for those deadly plant killers!

Hungry Hungry Henry was made for Dogpit's Cultivation Jam Due to time constraints, Henry's quest for sustenance is filled with bugs! but we hope that you'll enjoy the game anyway :D (If you're stuck at the title screen, please refresh the page)
